---
title: Cajun Chicken and Colcannon with green peas and garlic butter sauce
description: Cajun cooking collides with Irish cuisine in this fabulous fusion dish. Spiced chicken breast tops a bed of colcannon with a scattering of vibrant green peas thrown in for good measure. A hearty and flavourful option for dinner this week!
